    {
        "content": "<p>i'm disappointed that <code>mkAppM</code> doesn't accept a quoted lambda, like <code>\\</code>\\`(fun x y =&gt; x + y)<code>. forcing me to define </code>def plus ...<code> outside of scope (for some reason it also didn't allow the use of a local </code>let`)</p>",
